      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The engine and transmission are solid, but the exterior shows its age with some minor door dings, paint chips on the front bumper, and light scratching consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat bolster and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It has been recently serviced, though it will likely need new tires and a brake pad replacement within the next few months.",
